---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy — TagSmith"
	description="TagSmith privacy policy: all gamer tag generation happens locally in your browser, nothing is uploaded or stored."
	canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
		<h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#2B2013]">
			Privacy Policy
		</h1>
		<div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[#5C4F3D]">
			<p>
				Gamer tags generated in TagSmith are assembled entirely on your own
				device, inside your browser, from a hardcoded word list. Nothing is
				ever uploaded to, or stored on, any server operated by TagSmith.
			</p>
			<p>
				TagSmith uses standard web analytics to understand aggregate traffic
				(page views, referrers) and may display advertising through Google
				AdSense, which can set its own cookies subject to Google's own
				privacy policy.
			</p>
			<p>
				If you have questions about this policy, contact us via the details
				on the About page.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
